#. <section class="sutta" id="an7.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.2:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Dhanavagga"
msgstr "1. Wealth"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Dutiyapiyasutta"
msgstr "2. Pleasing (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an7.2:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ appiyo ca "
"hoti amanāpo ca agaru ca abhāvanīyo ca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities is disliked and disapproved by "
"their spiritual companions, not respected or admired."

msgctxt "an7.2:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu lābhakāmo ca hoti, sakkārakāmo ca hoti, "
"anavaññattikāmo ca hoti, ahiriko ca hoti, anottappī ca, issukī ca, maccharī "
"ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant desires material possessions, honor, and to be looked "
"up to. They lack conscience and prudence. They’re envious and mean."

msgctxt "an7.2:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ "
"appiyo ca hoti amanāpo ca agaru ca abhāvanīyo ca."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these seven qualities is disliked and disapproved by their "
"spiritual companions, not respected or admired."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an7.2:2.1"
msgid ""
"Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ piyo ca "
"hoti manāpo ca garu ca bhāvanīyo ca."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with seven qualities is liked and approved by their spiritual "
"companions, respected and admired."

msgctxt "an7.2:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi?"
msgstr "What seven?"

msgctxt "an7.2:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu na lābhakāmo ca hoti, na sakkārakāmo ca hoti, na "
"anavaññattikāmo ca hoti, hirīmā ca hoti, ottappī ca, anissukī ca, amaccharī "
"ca."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant doesn’t desire material possessions, honor, and to be "
"looked up to. They have conscience and prudence. They’re not envious or mean."

msgctxt "an7.2:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu sabrahmacārīnaṃ "
"piyo ca hoti manāpo ca garu ca bhāvanīyo cā”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these seven qualities is liked and approved by their "
"spiritual companions, respected and admired.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.2:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
